   <text>
      <body>
         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>Apollonides to Zenon, greeting. Please (pay back to Kriton?) his ex- penditure upon the fifty-mina mattresses if you have received them from him and if they are very good for you. (I have given?) to Apollonios the letter which Kriton brought. And now (please forward) to him the letters which Rhodon is bringing in order that (I may pay the workmen?) their wages complete.</ab>
         </div>
